name: $family
desc: Returns: The family of an organism shall be specified.

name: $genus
desc: Returns: The genus of an organism shall be specified; refers to the Latin epithet of the genus element of the plant/animal scientific name; it is present in names for genera, species and infraspecies.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The genus of an organism shall be specified; refers to the Latin epithet of the genus element of the plant/animal scientific name; it is present in names for genera, species and infraspecies.

name: $species
desc: Returns: The species of an organism shall be specified; refers to the Latin epithet of the species of the plant/animal; it is present in names for species and infraspecies.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The species of an organism shall be specified; refers to the Latin epithet of the species of the plant/animal; it is present in names for species and infraspecies.

name: $intraspecificType
desc: Returns: The Intraspecific type of an organism shall be specified.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The Intraspecific type of an organism shall be specified.

name: $intraspecificDescription
desc: Returns: The intraspecific description of an organism shall be specified based on a controlled vocabulary. For Influenza Vaccine, the intraspecific description shall contain the syntax of the antigen in line with the WHO convention.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The intraspecific description of an organism shall be specified based on a controlled vocabulary. For Influenza Vaccine, the intraspecific description shall contain the syntax of the antigen in line with the WHO convention.
